'''Hue Help''' is a registered charity number 1117116 in England and Wales<ref>http://www.charity-commission.gov.uk/Showcharity/RegisterOfCharities/CharityWithoutPartB.aspx?RegisteredCharityNumber=1117116&SubsidiaryNumber=0 Charity Commission for England and Wales</ref> and is a registered International Non-Governmental Organisation in Vietnam.<ref>http://www.ngocentre.org.vn/ingodirectory VUFO INGO Directory</ref> The organisation runs charitable programmes in [[Thua Thien Hue]], [[Vietnam]]. Programmes include supporting a home for poor children, providing swimming tuition for children in flood zones<ref>http://www.educare.edu.vn/tintuc/Home/ViewDetail/1841 Educare.News - In Vietnamese</ref> and operating an international volunteer programme.<ref>http://www.idealist.org/view/volop/S2wsPpcTFDw4 Idealist</ref>

