jardins-Proulx |first1=P |last2=White |first2=EP |last3=Adamson |first3=JJ |last4=Ram |first4=K |last5=Poisot |first5=T |last6=Gravel|first6=D |year=2013 |title=The Case for Open Preprints in Biology |journal=[[PLoS Biology]] |volume=11 |issue=5 |pages=e1001563 |doi=10.1371/journal.pbio.1001563 |doi-access=free |pmid=23690752 |pmc=3653830 }}
